description: The Bloomberg Euro Corporate Bond Index aims to reflect the performance of the following market: EUR-denominated corporate bonds Investment grade bonds only Bonds with maturities of at least 1 year Minimum amount outstanding of EUR 300 million per bond Additional information on the Index and the general methodology behind the Bloomberg indices can be found on Bloomberg index website ( https://www.bloombergindices.com/ ).
name: Xtrackers II EUR Corporate Bond UCITS ETF 1C
